PrecisSetting aside of the election of RONALD SUNSHINE, who was elected to the office of CHIEF by the STURGEON LAKE BAND OF INDIANS in Alberta on August 28, 1991, as well as the election of seven other councillors, due to a violation of subsection 77(1) of the Indian Act which might have affected the results of that election.
Attachments
precis:
Setting aside of the election of RONALD SUNSHINE, who was elected to the
office of CHIEF by the STURGEON LAKE BAND OF INDIANS in Alberta on
August 28, 1991, as well as the election of seven other councillors, due to
a violation of subsection 77(1) of the Indian Act which might have affected
the results of that election.
